post1.title: Quickplan
post1.content: Stage 1: . Create a simple toolkit to load data on . Timesheets . | Cost rates . | Projects . | Employees . | . | Use some nice model to make “effort prediction” (I think loading timesheet data for couple years will give enough insights for a simple model). Nothing complex or fancy, but let’s have some “know how” . | Write a post/article and publish it (own website + some good places) . This is about coming clean and simple, not about the “new era for ERP” | . | . Stage 2: . Generalize a toolkit (world data, economics) . | Make a bigger toolkit . Dashboards . | Integration . | A place to make it a proper GPL library . | . | .
